text: Ðys syndon ða landgemare ðe syndon on ðese ealdan bec awritene.
Ærest onlong Foss on ða hocihtan dic.
Of ðere hocihtan dic on ðone bradan þorn.
Onlong Foss on ðene fulan ford.
Of langaforda on Wenric ongean streame.
Of Wenric on ða grenan dic.
Of ðere dic on ða bradan strette.
Of ðere strætte on ða grenan dic.
Onlong þere dic ðæt eft on Foss.
